Albert Hellstern is a graduate of Harvard University, where he earned a Bachelor of Science degree in 1981; he also holds a Master's Degree in International Studies from Stanford University (1985).  Mr. Hellstern was hired as Assistant Business Manager in 1993 and was promoted to Business Manager shortly thereafter.  Although Mr. Hellstern is a native speaker of English, he speaks German, French and Spanish with equal fluency.  Mr. Hellstern has travelled extensively in South America and is responsible for establishing our company's presence there.